<div class="container py-5">
  <div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-md-10">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-body p-5">
          <h1 class="mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
          <p class="lead">Last Updated: April 25, 2025</p>
          
          <p>
            This Privacy Policy describes how Aquire Bot ("we", "us", or "our") collects, uses, and shares 
            your information when you use our Discord bot and dashboard services.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="mt-5 mb-3">Information We Collect</h2>
          
          <h3 class="mt-4 mb-2">Information Collected Automatically</h3>
          <p>
            When you use Aquire Bot in your Discord server, we automatically collect certain information, including:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Server ID and server name</li>
            <li>Channel IDs and channel names</li>
            <li>User IDs and usernames of server members who interact with the bot</li>
            <li>Bot command usage statistics</li>
            <li>Bot configuration settings for your server</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h3 class="mt-4 mb-2">Information You Provide</h3>
          <p>
            We collect information you provide directly to us when using Aquire Bot, including:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Custom welcome messages, auto-responses, and other configuration settings</li>
            <li>Suggestions and feedback submitted via the bot</li>
            <li>Economy data (virtual currency balances and transaction history)</li>
            <li>Reminders and their associated messages</li>
            <li>Application responses (when using the applications feature)</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h3 class="mt-4 mb-2">Dashboard Information</h3>
          <p>
            When you use our web dashboard, we collect:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Your Discord account information (ID, username, avatar, email) via Discord OAuth</li>
            <li>Servers you manage</li>
            <li>Dashboard preferences and settings</li>
            <li>Session data for authentication</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2 class="mt-5 mb-3">How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p>
            We use the information we collect to:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Provide, maintain, and improve Aquire Bot services</li>
            <li>Configure the bot according to your server preferences</li>
            <li>Save and retrieve user data for economy and other features</li>
            <li>Track command usage for optimization and debugging</li>
            <li>Authenticate you on the dashboard</li>
            <li>Respond to your requests and support inquiries</li>
            <li>Monitor and analyze usage patterns and trends</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2 class="mt-5 mb-3">Data Storage and Security</h2>
          <p>
            We store all collected data in a secure MongoDB database. We implement appropriate technical and organizational 
            measures to protect your data against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction.
          </p>
          <p>
            Data is retained as long as the bot is in your server or as needed to provide you with our services. 
            You may request deletion of your data at any time.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="mt-5 mb-3">Sharing Your Information</h2>
          <p>
            We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your information to third parties. We may share information in the 
            following circumstances:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>With third-party service providers who perform services on our behalf (e.g., hosting providers)</li>
            <li>If required by law or in response to valid legal process</li>
            <li>To protect our rights, privacy, safety, or property</li>
            <li>In connection with a merger, acquisition, or sale of assets</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2 class="mt-5 mb-3">Your Rights and Choices</h2>
          <p>
            You have the right to:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Access, update, or delete your personal information</li>
            <li>Object to processing of your personal information</li>
            <li>Withdraw consent at any time (by removing the bot from your server)</li>
            <li>Request a copy of the data we hold about you</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            To exercise these rights, please contact us through our support server.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="mt-5 mb-3">Children's Privacy</h2>
          <p>
            Aquire Bot is not intended for use by individuals under the age of 13, or the applicable age of digital consent 
            in your country. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under these ages.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="mt-5 mb-3">Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
          <p>
            We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify users of any significant changes by posting 
            an announcement in our support server and updating the "Last Updated" date at the top of this policy.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="mt-5 mb-3">Contact Us</h2>
          <p>
            If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please join our 
            <a href="https://discord.gg/invite" target="_blank">support server</a> to contact us.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

